  <p>
    A <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">three-phase disc stack centrifuge</a> separates the liquid stream into fats and water in subsequent processes.
  </p>

  <figure>
    <img
      src="/images/decanter-centrifuge-applications/Alfa-Laval-NX-314-Decanter-Centrifuge-Module-for-WVO-Processing.webp"
      alt="Alfa Laval NX-314 Decanter Centrifuge Module for WVO Processing"
      class="img-cap-600"
